Average Price Sheet 11

1. Right Click the Total Volume Select Duplicate . Rename the Sheet as Avg Price  remove Total Volume form Marks card


2. Drag and drop Average Price to Text  under Marks. Rt click the Average price and from the drop-down menu select Measure Average. From the menu bar click on Entire View from the Drop-down list



3.Click on Text and then click on the ellipses Select the Text  > Font Type Tableau Bold >Font Size :12 Bold >  Alignment :Center .

and select Alignment and select Horizontal Center and Vertical Center



4. Right click on Total Volume and select Format



5. Go to pane under Default Select Numbers ,Custom Numbers, Decimal Places 2 and Prefix as $.


6. Rt click on title and erase everything and enter Avg Price> Tableau Semi bold > Font size 10 > Bold > Align center.


7. From the Menu bar at the top select the option for viewing and from the drop down select Entire View.
